ZH: 我今天骑自行车去了公园。
EN: I rode my bicycle to the park today.

ZH: 她喜欢骑自行车到处走走。
EN: She likes to ride her bicycle around.

ZH: 孩子们在学校附近骑自行车。
EN: The children ride their bicycles near the school.

ZH: 我的自行车需要修理。
EN: My bicycle needs repair.

ZH: 我们计划明天去自行车旅行。
EN: We plan to go on a bicycle trip tomorrow.

ZH: 她的自行车被偷了。
EN: Her bicycle was stolen.

ZH: 你可以借我一辆自行车吗？
EN: Can I borrow your bicycle?

ZH: 我的自行车很旧了，我得换一辆新的。
EN: My bicycle is very old, I need to get a new one.

ZH: 我很喜欢在海边骑自行车。
EN: I enjoy riding my bicycle by the seashore.

ZH: 昨天下雨，所以我没骑自行车去工作。
EN: It rained yesterday, so I didn't ride my bicycle to work.

ZH: 我每天早上骑自行车锻炼身体。
EN: I ride my bicycle every morning to exercise.

ZH: 他们准备好了自行车装备。
EN: They are ready with their bicycle gear.

ZH: 我的自行车胎爆了，我得修理一下。
EN: My bicycle tire burst, I need to fix it.

ZH: 我最喜欢的运动之一就是骑自行车。
EN: One of my favorite sports is riding a bicycle.

ZH: 警察带走了他偷的自行车。
EN: The police took away the bicycle he stole.

ZH: 我们租了自行车游览整个城市。
EN: We rented bicycles to explore the entire city.

ZH: 这辆自行车很贵，但是非常好用。
EN: This bicycle is expensive, but very good quality.

ZH: 昨天我买了一辆新自行车。
EN: I bought a new bicycle yesterday.

ZH: 他坐在自行车后面让母亲骑。
EN: He sat on the back of the bicycle and let his mother ride.

ZH: 我们在海边租了自行车，沿着海岸骑行。
EN: We rented bicycles by the seaside and rode along the coast.
